HEADWORD: Nemophily
<hw>Ne*moph"i*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>ne`mos</grk> wooded pasture, glade + <grk>filei^n</grk> to
love.]</ety> <def>Fondness for forest scenery; love of the woods.</def>
